Class JacksonFeatures

  • java.lang.Object

    JsonFeatures

    @Internal
public final class JacksonFeatures
extends Object
implements JsonFeatures
    Stores features to later configure an ObjectMapper. Features are supplied through the JacksonFeatures annotation.
